NAME
    Sledge::Plugin::Template::Plugin::Comma - auto use
    Template::Plugin::Comma

SYNOPSIS
      # in pages
      package Your::Pages;
      use Sledge::Plugin::Template::Plugin::Comma;

      # in templates
      [% 355555 | comma %]

DESCRIPTION
    Auto use Template::Plugin::Comma.

